Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.87,0:00:03.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The inside of the heart is a mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.67,0:00:05.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stars and snow are all around us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.58,0:00:06.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Valentine's Day is almost here!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.21,0:00:08.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would you like a case with those chocolates?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.21,0:00:10.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seeing through to the one and only truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.76,0:00:12.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I look like a child, but have the intellect of an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.47,0:00:14.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My name is Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.64,0:01:51.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right around the time people start getting over the New Year's fever...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.82,0:01:56.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Girls begin to pour their hearts into a bittersweet gift of giri or honmei chocolates.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.82,0:01:56.11,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Giri chocolates are obligatory gifts to friends and colleagues, while honmei chocolates are gifts for boyfriends, husbands, or potential lovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.65,0:01:57.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, that's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.45,0:02:07.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Truth Behind Valentine's\N(Case Part)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.25,0:02:11.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's so great about Valentine's Day? It's just nonsense...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.38,0:02:15.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone just falls for the candy companies' marketing hype...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.67,0:02:18.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, people are always happy to receive candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.97,0:02:20.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chocolate tastes so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.18,0:02:24.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're complaining because you know you won't get any, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.60,0:02:26.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.98,0:02:30.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Being in this body means I'll only get the kind of chocolates meant for babies.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.94,0:02:34.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, in a way, Edogawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.69,0:02:39.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Japanese are the only people who get all lovey-dovey saying "chocolate this, chocolate that..."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.66,0:02:46.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No one seems to realize that Valentine's Day was named in memory of Saint Valentine, who died a gruesome death.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.91,0:02:49.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.29,0:02:50.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, my mom told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.46,0:02:57.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Valentine's Day is when girls create precious memories by professing their love through chocolates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.05,0:03:00.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why chocolate can be both sweet and bitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.30,0:03:04.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, did you buy any chocolates for your "special someone," Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.43,0:03:07.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, my dad said I'm still too young for that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.64,0:03:11.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it is too early for kids like you to be worrying about love...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.69,0:03:12.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.56,0:03:15.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about that girl back at the Detective Agency?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.36,0:03:17.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.78,0:03:23.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's excited that we're lodging at the Suito House tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.24,0:03:25.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, she never mentioned anything about chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.83,0:03:26.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.99,0:03:31.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, let's just pray that there won't be another case of "Bloody Valentine's"...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.12,0:03:33.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.17,0:03:36.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bloody Valentine's was the day when...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.59,0:03:46.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Al Capone shot down seven people with machine guns as they stood in front of a garage on February 14, 1929.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.31,0:03:49.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Capone?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.81,0:03:52.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that I think about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.02,0:03:57.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that guy said he was from the same town as Capone...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.53,0:04:01.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, you're gonna get left behind
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.24,0:04:02.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.70,0:04:04.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Conan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.07,0:04:06.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, Haibara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, chocolate is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.75,0:04:12.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.83,0:04:17.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why do we have to go all the way to a lodge deep in the mountains just to make sweets?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.67,0:04:20.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's so we can become good brides. Good brides.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.76,0:04:24.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe so, but couldn't you do that just as well at home?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.34,0:04:26.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now... Don't worry, don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.39,0:04:30.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, you never told me we were making sweets.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.10,0:04:33.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You said we would get to see lots of cute mountain animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.73,0:04:35.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh? You didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.69,0:04:41.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Suito House is famous for making chocolates that will make you lucky in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.57,0:04:42.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.32,0:04:48.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, you're going to make homemade chocolates for Kyogoku{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and finally confess your feelings to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.37,0:04:51.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah... At least that was my plan...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.50,0:04:55.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Sonoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.92,0:05:00.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He hasn't called lately, Makoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.51,0:05:04.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, I always get his answering machine when I call him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.09,0:05:06.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.09,0:05:14.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I called and told him I'd make Valentine chocolates and give them "to the person I like most."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.48,0:05:18.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was my "love-love strategy" after I failed in knitting a sweater for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.11,0:05:20.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's in for it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.36,0:05:23.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I should've came right out and said, "This chocolate is for you."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.69,0:05:26.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'll be okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.24,0:05:29.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you give him those chocolates, I'm sure Kyogoku{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} will...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.08,0:05:32.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're strong, Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.62,0:05:33.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.12,0:05:38.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm falling apart after not being able to talk to him for only a week...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.88,0:05:40.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, it seems like forever with Shinichi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.05,0:05:42.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A little...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.05,0:05:44.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, I've gotten used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.67,0:05:48.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter that he's not around...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.22,0:05:49.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.81,0:05:57.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.10,0:05:59.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're here to make chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.81,0:06:01.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please take care of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.27,0:06:04.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, granny, so you're the one...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.28,0:06:12.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the owner of this lodge, who tricked my girls into coming out to the mountains just to make sweets.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.58,0:06:14.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,D-Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.25,0:06:17.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm terribly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.46,0:06:19.00,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Yuasa Chiyoko (61)\NLodge Owner
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.17,0:06:20.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whether it's a trick or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.88,0:06:26.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Couples have come here to make chocolates for the past ten years, and end up getting married later on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.01,0:06:30.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The stories in magazines and on TV just exaggerated things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.01,0:06:34.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After my husband, the previous owner, died four years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.47,0:06:41.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mononoke{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} started appearing and has caused the number of guests to steadily decline.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.36,0:06:43.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mononoke{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.15,0:06:49.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, if a snow storm comes, don't go outside by yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.32,0:06:56.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unless you want to get strange gifts from the Mononoke that lives in these mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.83,0:06:59.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Strange gifts?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.50,0:07:02.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She means the chocolates!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.67,0:07:08.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These mountains are quite difficult to navigate, and accidents happen often.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.63,0:07:13.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Especially during this time of year, chocolates are always found lying atop the snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.60,0:07:16.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next to the bodies of those who died there, that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.10,0:07:18.68,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Nigaki Yoshitaka (28)\NLodge Guest
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.68,0:07:26.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Some say it's the ghost of a woman who came to this lodge to make chocolates, but got lost in the woods and died.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.40,0:07:31.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Other rumors say it's the doing of the Yuki-onna.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.49,0:07:33.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yu-Yuki-onna?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.58,0:07:37.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, there's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.87,0:07:41.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The police said wild animals scavenge through the victim's belongings looking for food.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.25,0:07:48.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, they said it's a coincidence that there are always chocolates around the bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.63,0:07:53.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm heading off to work now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.22,0:07:54.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.18,0:07:56.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nigaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.93,0:08:00.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's good to be a hard worker...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.10,0:08:01.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, please don't get lost in the woods.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.10,0:08:05.06,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Konakawa Mika (26)\NLodge Guest
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.98,0:08:05.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the Yuki-onna finds you, it could be very bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.82,0:08:08.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'll be alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.53,0:08:12.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the Yuki-onna wants to give me some chocolates, I'll just tell her this...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.20,0:08:16.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I already have a girlfriend, and her name is Ako!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.53,0:08:21.00,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Amari Ako (25)\NLodge Guest
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.12,0:08:21.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't, Yoshitaka. It's embarrassing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.58,0:08:24.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.71,0:08:26.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.50,0:08:28.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it, little boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.92,0:08:32.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That guy said he's going to work, but what's he going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.68,0:08:35.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's a reporter who's going to film and take some pictures...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.10,0:08:43.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...so he can use them as evidence in the case he's been working on for five years.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.77,0:08:54.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At first, I was the one who followed him with the camera, but he said I would've definitely seen something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.70,0:08:58.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Seen something?" You don't mean the Yuki-onna, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.12,0:09:03.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not it! He wants to take pictures of a certain animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.21,0:09:08.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, right now, it seems it's as much a myth as the Yuki-onna.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.21,0:09:10.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Myth?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.38,0:09:13.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.63,0:09:19.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After one was found dead in 1905, there hasn't been a verifiable sighting of one in over 100 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.55,0:09:19.18,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Sagami Yuusou (42)\NLodge Guest
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.47,0:09:23.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's an animal that's on the red list of endangered species.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.85,0:09:25.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The legendary Japanese Wolf!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.85,0:09:28.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A wolf?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.86,0:09:31.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, is that okay to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.82,0:09:34.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hunting such an endangered species...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.24,0:09:37.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, this gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.36,0:09:42.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm only going to use this rifle to lure the wolf into a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.75,0:09:48.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, ma'am, I leave my friend in your care.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.05,0:09:56.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Time and time again, we get visitors who think about nothing but hunting wolves...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.43,0:09:59.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess I'll go out for a while, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.05,0:10:04.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If anyone else shows up, please take them to an empty guest room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.98,0:10:09.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Granny, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.90,0:10:14.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to visit my husband's grave in the woods.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.78,0:10:17.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it okay to go by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.61,0:10:20.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This forest is like my garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.03,0:10:23.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, Saburo is coming with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.20,0:10:24.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saburo?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.29,0:10:33.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There, there... What a good boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.34,0:10:35.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the...? It's a dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.34,0:10:42.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hope that reporter doesn't mistake your dog as the wolf if he sees it in the woods.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.68,0:10:47.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not possible. He saw-the wolf around 10:00 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.06,0:10:49.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, what does that have to do with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.40,0:10:53.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saburo isn't allowed outside after dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.15,0:10:55.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.19,0:11:01.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, while she's out, how about we get started on making some chocolates?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.20,0:11:03.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.49,0:11:06.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Isn't that old lady supposed to teach them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.54,0:11:09.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was how it was done in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.33,0:11:13.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're the ones who teach the guests now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.67,0:11:16.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's to thank her for taking care of us each year.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.09,0:11:22.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, she continues to prepare the ingredients to this day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.64,0:11:23.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.60,0:11:29.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like your "love strategy" or whatever might fail again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.35,0:11:30.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up, old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.31,0:11:35.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Valentine's is in three days!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.15,0:11:37.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's get a move on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.03,0:11:41.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.66,0:11:48.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, Granny's husband died in an avalanche?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.16,0:11:49.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thats right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.33,0:11:51.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was four years ago, on February 14th.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.46,0:11:57.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They said it had been a week before Saburo found him buried in the snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.25,0:12:02.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, the other body hasn't been found yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.80,0:12:04.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"The other body?"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.39,0:12:06.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My brother's.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.18,0:12:09.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He went missing on the same day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.89,0:12:17.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The police said his body is still buried somewhere in the snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.57,0:12:20.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, I get the feeling he's still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.61,0:12:28.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Other than visiting the previous owner's grave, that's why I've been coming here every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.04,0:12:31.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for telling you such a sad story.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.71,0:12:33.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.71,0:12:37.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, is there anything we can do to help?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.79,0:12:40.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, no! Men aren't allowed in the kitchen!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.13,0:12:43.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll end up get hurt just like Nigaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} did!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.80,0:12:45.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.56,0:12:52.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I did it! It's complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.64,0:12:54.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lovely!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.73,0:12:57.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks so good, it looks so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.65,0:12:58.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It really does.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.99,0:13:10.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, should we take a group picture with your chocolates?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.24,0:13:11.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.59,0:13:21.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like a snow storm's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.17,0:13:24.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Nigaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} is all right...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.76,0:13:29.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, we're going out for a little while to check up on Nigaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.55,0:13:30.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.68,0:13:31.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.06,0:13:34.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oya, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.60,0:13:36.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.61,0:13:42.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nigaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.36,0:13:44.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where are you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.82,0:13:46.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nigaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.54,0:14:01.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't find Nigaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} anywhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.67,0:14:06.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we split up to look for him, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.22,0:14:09.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The storm's getting worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.59,0:14:12.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, let's go search for him before the probability of finding him is zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.56,0:14:16.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, wait here in the lodge.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.81,0:14:22.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like I'd do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.07,0:14:24.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Saburo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.71,0:14:47.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yoshitaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.42,0:14:49.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nigaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.47,0:14:50.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nigaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.55,0:14:53.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.35,0:14:54.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nigaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.14,0:14:57.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where are you, Nigaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.68,0:15:00.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Answer us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.69,0:15:01.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.11,0:15:03.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nigaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.40,0:15:08.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A gun shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.70,0:15:11.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, this is bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.32,0:15:14.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did he kill it before me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.28,0:15:17.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.45,0:15:22.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me? I'm a guest who's lodging at the Suito House.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.21,0:15:23.58,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Itakura Hajime (37)\NLodge Guest
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.13,0:15:29.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.88,0:15:31.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where are you, Nigaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.51,0:15:36.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Saburo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.14,0:15:41.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nigaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.36,0:15:49.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's no use, he's no longer breathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.28,0:15:51.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was beaten to death?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.61,0:15:54.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.83,0:15:59.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.75,0:16:00.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...a chocolate?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.29,0:16:05.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yoshitaka, please answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.34,0:16:09.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not good, the snow storm has gotten stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.71,0:16:11.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.67,0:16:17.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we continue searching in this, we'll be putting ourselves in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.26,0:16:20.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B-But, we can't just leave Nigaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} out here...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.14,0:16:22.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.14,0:16:24.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So deep in the mountains...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.02,0:16:26.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be Saburo?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.81,0:16:30.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That can't be! Saburo is supposed to be at the lodge.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.49,0:16:32.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be that Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.45,0:16:43.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!? What are doing out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.33,0:16:45.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you to stay at the lodge?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.13,0:16:47.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.71,0:16:48.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, look...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.71,0:16:58.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't Mika{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} tell us that Saburo found the previous owner, even though he was buried in the snow?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.35,0:16:59.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.56,0:17:07.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I thought he could help us find Nigaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.73,0:17:13.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nigaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} has come to this lodge several times before, so Saburo should know his scent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.82,0:17:16.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, did you find Nigaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.20,0:17:20.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I found him,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.83,0:17:22.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but it's already too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.87,0:17:23.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.50,0:17:31.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.55,0:17:33.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a lie... Right, Yoshitaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.92,0:17:34.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yoshitaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.55,0:17:35.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stay where you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.72,0:17:38.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look! There's blood on his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.97,0:17:43.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And there's a blood-covered stick laying next to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.89,0:17:45.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.14,0:17:46.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a murder case.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.10,0:17:51.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Until we find the murderer, we shouldn't disturb the crime scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.36,0:17:53.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Murder...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.48,0:17:54.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.90,0:17:59.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're awfully cocky for someone who's not with the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.66,0:18:06.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's true I'm not with the police anymore, but I'm a former officer, detective Mouri Kogoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.66,0:18:07.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.08,0:18:09.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri, as in...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.75,0:18:11.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That famous detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.13,0:18:15.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, do you know who the murderer is?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.67,0:18:16.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.97,0:18:22.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With the weather like this, it's difficult to get an accurate time of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.31,0:18:25.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, the murderer's footprints have been covered up by the snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.64,0:18:32.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All I can gather is that the murderer's clothes should have Nigaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s blood on them,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.44,0:18:36.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and that Nigaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was most likely killed in the afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.49,0:18:43.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The blood on Nigaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s face has been wiped off in one area,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.37,0:18:51.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the sunglasses he's wearing indicate that he was killed before sunset.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.71,0:18:58.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After that time, it would be too dangerous to wear sunglasses and walk around in this dark snow storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.67,0:19:01.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see. As expected of a famous detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.01,0:19:04.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, this is nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.06,0:19:07.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not too tough for a good investigator like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.18,0:19:08.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you really sure about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.23,0:19:10.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez... Not this kid again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.90,0:19:14.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why you need to look carefully into his sunglasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.90,0:19:18.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, you can see that his left contact lens is out of place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.61,0:19:19.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.03,0:19:22.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That must have happened when the murderer hit him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.37,0:19:27.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, there's no contact lens in his right eye, and it's not in his sunglasses either.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.37,0:19:30.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.46,0:19:32.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.12,0:19:35.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When he was hit, his right contact lens and glasses fell off,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.42,0:19:39.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but the criminal only noticed the sunglasses, and put them back on the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.63,0:19:43.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see. This sure is one elaborate criminal...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.01,0:19:46.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't misunderstand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.26,0:19:49.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, isn't it possible that the criminal did that intentionally?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.85,0:19:52.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.52,0:19:55.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, what reasons would they have for doing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.98,0:19:58.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah... I also found something strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.65,0:20:00.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See? It's a chocolate!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.78,0:20:04.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was on this guy's lap.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.87,0:20:08.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It has "Yoshi" is written on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.70,0:20:09.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.37,0:20:12.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, that's the chocolate Ako made today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.46,0:20:16.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why!? Why is my chocolate here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.00,0:20:20.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't you put it there next to the body?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.05,0:20:26.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's impossible for Ako{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, because the chocolate was in the kitchen before we all left the lodge.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.01,0:20:31.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Both before and after that, Ako{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} had always been with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.89,0:20:34.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, who brought the chocolate all the way out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.02,0:20:37.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was probably the criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.48,0:20:40.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since we already know they've tampered with the body...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.94,0:20:45.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...there's a high probability that they put the chocolate here to frame Ako{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.66,0:20:50.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, the first thing we should do is to head back to the lodge and call the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.75,0:20:53.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The police won't be able to come for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.25,0:20:57.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Sagami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}! How did you know we were here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.29,0:21:00.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just followed the sound of the dog barking.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.88,0:21:04.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You said that the police can't come, what do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.34,0:21:13.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The tunnel that links the lodge to the road was blocked off by an avalanche about 30 minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.98,0:21:18.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'll probably be a day or so before it can be reopened.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.77,0:21:19.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.61,0:21:20.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.69,0:21:25.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, does that mean we have to spend the night at the lodge, even while the culprit roams around freely?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.41,0:21:31.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The criminal who killed Nigaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} could even be among us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.25,0:21:35.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't have a problem with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.75,0:21:37.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's more of a thrill that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.83,0:21:45.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you don't want to stay with us, you can sit next to the corpse all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.68,0:21:51.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, by the time morning comes, you'll have frozen and turned into the Yuki-onna.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.77,0:22:00.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The remaining blood that wasn't wiped off,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.52,0:22:03.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the repositioned sunglasses,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.32,0:22:08.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and then Ako{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s chocolate...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.70,0:22:15.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did the culprit go through all the trouble of bringing Ako{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s chocolate from the lodge?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.26,0:23:51.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This picture was taken right after Nigaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} was beaten.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.38,0:23:55.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.22,0:23:55.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That reminds me...
